author: Times Of India
title: Courage, faith helped beat virus: 103-yr-old Italian
description: “I'm well, I'm well,” Zanusso said during a video call from the Maria Grazia Residence for the elderly in Lessona. “I watch TV, read the newspapers.” Zanusso said. The virus has killed nearly 18,000 people in Italy.
